nd we used to be out in the morning on a milk round, or perhaps a paper round and - we had to help mother see. And if we were lucky in regards to pocket money, if father was not at work we never got any but if he was at work well we might get a halfpenny 
we might get a penny. And we thought the world of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What would you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 We could get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 ha'porth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  of sweets, or go in the baker shop and ask if they had got a stale cake for a halfpenny or penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were there actually shops near here then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh in King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}College Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, yes. But of course some of the shops, like not only my mother, a good many more, the expenses was too much for their pockets although they weren't so dear as now, but we used to have to make way for Queens Crescent.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 For cheaper shopping, or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Camden{\*\xmlclose} 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Town{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Markets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 That's right, yes. And we had to walk .. There were no buses in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 It's a long way!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 It was. Buses never run up {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Adelaide Road{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} in those days. The horse buses used to stop at Chalk Farm. Then we got to walk, well we never rode because we couldn't afford it. And eventually buses got up to Eton Rise do they call it now? Or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Eton Place{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, the public house. Yes, well they got as far as there. The horses. Of course when the motors began to come in well they extended. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How old were you when you started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 When I started school? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  year}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  old. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Whereabouts was the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, I went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Winchester Road{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}, for a while, (5 miles away) {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}St. Paul}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 {\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s. Then I broke away from there and went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}All{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Souls{\*\xmlclose} 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}School{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Fairhazel{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Gardens{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}. (further away)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Why did you move?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well the teacher was a bit severe. Yes. In fact really put fear into you. The headmaster. Oh he was, very strict. Yes. Of course I broke away from there see. But most of the others went to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}St. Paul{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}'s School, finished there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was it a fairly big school in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}St. Paul{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}'s? No, same as}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177  it\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  now. In fact not so big. Because that front has been added to it. That wasn't there not in my days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did you enjoy school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well yes, I can't say, I didn't. Course we had women teachers down at All Soul's School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 They weren't as strict?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No. Not quite so strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did you prefer it at All Soul's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes. Definitely yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How far away is it? How many minutes walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, for me now, in those days you could do it in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid405605\charrsid10295177 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Not too far then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You would have lunch at home then would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes. There was no school meals in those days. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Had you any school outings at all?
