Well not really, the only outing we used to get, well you might get one from Sunday School and our Band of Hope, which was down here, we might get taken on Primrose Hill and we used to think the world of it, for an outing. And if}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177  funds were better}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  we might go to Chorley Wood.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Where is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, I don't know what county that comes in really. Whether it comes in Middlesex -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Which Sunday School did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}St. Paul}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 {\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s. Yes. We 
used to go to Sunday School in the morning and after we had had the prayers and that we used to go onto the Church, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}St.{\*\xmlclose} Paul's, in Avenue Road. Of course that is not there now. That got bombed. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were your parents interested at all in Church or Chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
They weren't. But they saw that we went. Yes. Yes. They weren't non-religion, I don't mean that, well they couldn't, mother was too busy you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was your father interested in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no. My father, really couldn't read. In their days, schooling, well they didn't learn. Mother used to read the paper to him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Which paper did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh I can't recall that. I should think - I don't know, no I can't say. Of course we weren't allowed to read a newspaper. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Why not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 I don't know. My old people didn't believe in it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Had you any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Books? No. No. I remember the days when, going on to Swiss Cottage now, when the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 re }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 used to be chickens running about there. In the yard, do you
 know the Swiss Public House? Well in their yard was a stables, saddle house as they called them, well then they used to keep chickens in there. And they used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 un out in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Finchley Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} and Avenue Road, that was round, in Avenue Road where the old horse c
abs, the hackney carriages, well of course the chickens used to get out there for the food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 It seems incredible doesn't it now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 It does. It wouldn't do now would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Not with all the traffic at Swiss Cottage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Too true.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You said that you had a Band of Hope down here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. That was our Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Who organised it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well it was run by a man called Mr. Salmon. And of course he had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 1}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  friends and they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 were a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 lways together. And we used to go to the bottom of the news here and sing and he'd pray, and sometimes on King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}College Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Every Sunday and once in the week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Like on your photograph. Obviously lots of people went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, oh yes. They are mainly all dead and gone now of c
ourse. Oh yes, lot's of people went and the horse, there used to be the horse cabs down here and somebody, if the cab men were here, in the week, they used to join in. But there was no Sunday work here. No. Not in regards to the cabs going out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were they the Mews people who went?
