\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 F}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 rom the place out of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 M}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 ews what was, I don't know if they are still there or not, there was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 M}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
ews, I haven't been out for a long while, not around that way. Been rebuilt of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What other families were there all down this road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What were they worth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, what were they, what sort of jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 All different, well, they were all sorts. Milkmen. Gardeners.
 My uncle here was a chimney sweep. And my, well all sort of mixed up work, you know. There was a blacksmith down here. And there was also a builder}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s shop. And a carpenter}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s shop}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Quite a lot of things down a small road!
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 They were very neighbourly were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh very, very, very neighbourly. Different to what things are today. One would help the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 They would help out if you were out of work would they? Or ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well of course there was illness of course. And if
 you was out of work or ill well there was no money coming in. No. There was none of this insurance business. If you was out of work, well, as I keep saying, nothing was coming in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You did all these odd errands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, that's true, yes. And if you
 could get a job in the evening, course these houses in those days was one high family. You know, one house, one family. Horses and carriages. Maids, servants, you know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 
And if you could get a job in the evening, some of them would advertise for a boy to go and clean boots or silver, in the evening. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 We used to do that, if we could get a job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Had you much spare time then? Or were you always a bit busy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well there was always, there was spare time, but as I say you hadn't money was so poor that you was glad to get what few pence you could.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What sort of games would you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Oh skipping rope, rounders, tippy cat - I don't know if you know that do you? No, well, there used to be a piece of wood on the ground, and you make a peg, and you get a stick and hit that tippy on the point.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What was your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Milkman. On a Milk round. In {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Belsize Lane{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}, Hampstead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How did you find that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh it was very
 good really. Of course it was early morning, well we was brought up to get up in the mornings. Not laying in bed. And father would never have, we weren't allowed out late at night. No. My father would never, perhaps we would mean like children used to, "
Come on" he said "Bed. You can't burn the candle both ends no more than I can." That was his words. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Would you say that your parents were strict with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, I don't say, we had to do what we were told. Yes. But they weren't, what can I say, spiteful to us. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were they strict over manners at the table, that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, very. Father -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What had you got to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 As you sat at the table, at meals, you weren't allowed to talk over the table. No. If one would per
haps go on for a couple of seconds, father would say "You know where you are" of course we knew what he meant.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 If you were naughty were you punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well we were corrected. I can't say we were knocked about, we were corrected. Yes. You would ge
t a smack and upstairs to bed. And no answering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How did you like your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh very good indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was it all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, they were nice people. Very nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was it hard work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, medium.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How well paid was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How well paid? Oh I couldn't say. I don't know what I got. I think I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You gave your mother this did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How much spending money had you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well I might get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 18}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  pence or 2/-.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What would you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well. That depended of course on what you wanted. Course you see mother had to clothe us. And our boots and all that sort of thing. We couldn't buy it ourselves, well they couldn't give us the money to buy it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What was your milk round like? About how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh I stayed there I think, let me think where did I go from there? A two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Then I got another job, I am trying to think where I went to. I think it was on King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15758399\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}College Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. A greengrocer n
ame of Elliot. Of course that's gone long ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was it helping in the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 In the shop, and taking out orders. Yes. Well that was the main thing, taking out orders. Course the men done the work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You were still only a boy then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, what you might say shop boy. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well then I finished there, if I remember right I got a job at the yard here, horse keeping. In the cab yard. Yes. And then, they used to give the ho}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 rs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 es, some of them, used to be, go out for a rest, well I used to ride horses from here to Hatfield.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 That's a long way isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. Horses, you know, needed a rest. Then if there was, perhaps I might take }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 2 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 or I might take }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
. Ride one and tie the other. Well of course there wasn't the traffic that there is now, all horse traffic. And I may bring some back. If there were any to come back I would bring them back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Who owned them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 A man named Mr. Kemp. Well he did have some in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
Eton Place{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} too. Behind the Eton Hotel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 And were all those stables up and down here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes. Both sides of the mews. The other side and that side}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid999950\charrsid10295177  was}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  pulled down. And down the bottom. And right over the other mews.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Quite a big business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, yes it was. He was a church going man. He retired to Northwood. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 A good boss was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, very good indeed. Yes. Yes. He never interfered unnecessary as long as the work was done. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How long did you stop doing that then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well then, I think I stopped, I can't say what year they finished mind you, until they sold up, on account of the taxis come in}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 , of course, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 and took them over. It was a shame, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 I am trying to think that out now. Well then I went er, butchering. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 That was quite different wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh different altogether. Yes. But you soon got trained and used to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Why did you choose that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well it was the first job that come along, sort of thing. And Mr. Moore the Butcher, we were well-known, the family were well-known, and of co
urse he offered me the job, and of course I took it on. But the money was poor, I can't recall the money mind you,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177  I can\rquote t recall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  but the money was so poor, we used to have to buy our own smocks and aprons. Well if you hadn't got the money due they'd buy them and stop you so much a week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You learnt a trade then, more or less?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You learnt all about the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 The butchering? Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Whereabouts was the shop?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 In King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 s {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}College Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. No. 8.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Not so far away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
No. Well then I, I think, that's coming back to the 14 war now. Er, we broke away, we knew that we had got to go and so we went from there and joined up. Of course we went in the army and all that. Well then when I came home, I was wounded, wounded in the
 stomach, and I used to do market work then. Before I went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What was that? Which market was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, an every day in the week market. And as I say well in those days we used to pull out of this yard here half past }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  in the morning and work till }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  o'clock at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You must have been dead beat!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well yes. And work mind you, work. We all come home from market, we didn't all, there was t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  of us went to market, and we'd come home, unload, have breakfast then you'd got your rounds to do. I
n those days you used to go round and get orders. We used to carry a tray, a butcher's tray, on your shoulder, and they had ponies and carts also. You'd come back and do your lunch orders and get them, then round again with your, what they call dinner, la
te night orders. There was no such thing as half day a week. Oh no. The only early day you had was 5 o'clock on a Thursday night, you shut. On the Saturday we used to work same thing, if we had to go to market, but if we didn't go to market we started at 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15424190\charrsid10295177 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  and you were lucky if you were done at 11 or 12 o'clock at night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Gosh. I am surprised you stuck it!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well it was the usual thing, I mean, you never looked, there was no such thing as thinking you shouldn't do this and you shouldn't do that. And of course in those days the public houses used to be open until mid-night, open all day also.
