on he'd say again - you know where you boys are. Yes dad. You been to work? Yes dad. Well, finish - you've done}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10295177  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 wo
rk - finish it. That's what he'd say.
