\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, oh he would talk then, get away, but he used - it was always had manners to talk over the table - their idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 But with such a big family it would have been a noise wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were they particular about things like how you sat in your chair?
