\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 In a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How did they like you to sit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, sit ordinary - sit comfortable, you know what I mean. You hadn't got to lounge down and you - you weren't allowed to do that.

