\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, books - but not - we were never allowed to read a newspaper - in fact father couldn't read, mother used to read to him. Early days o
f course they - they never had schooling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What did she read to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Newspaper - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. The Sunday paper - not in the week, because we was - money couldn't go to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 They just had a Sunday paper did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Do you remember which it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 I think - I think the News of the World - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 If your mother gave you some food and you left any - I don't suppose that happened very often did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Suppose you did what would she say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well, she - she'd ask you what was wrong and if it was - they wouldn't force you to eat it - if they found you'd had enough but that wasn't thrown away mind you. It was mixed up for next day. Yes. Nothing was wasted because they couldn't afford it, no.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You mean even what was left on your plates was saved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. Yes. Providing it was saveable - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were you expected if she served something up - were you expected to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Could you pick and choose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh no, you had to have what you was given.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What she wanted you to have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How did she serve up the meal in those days - would she serve straight from the pots onto the plates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, straight from the pot - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Never into dishes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did you always have the same regular place that you sat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, it didn't matter where you sat as long as you ate, you know, you was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were people served in a certain order - was your father for example served first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Father was served first - oh yes, yes. Then mother would go round you know, whichever \'85...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 The way you were sitting - not in order of your ages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes - no, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 When you wanted to get down from the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 We'd ask - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did you have to wait until everyone had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, wait 'til we'd all finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 All get down together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 When you started did you all start together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. Yes, all started together.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 When there were younger brothers and sisters - little babies - were they fed at the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Same time - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 How did your mother manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, they sat on the floor really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 And she'd feed them a bit of something would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, got along very nicely everybody did - yes. She was all thoroughly known - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 And you felt close to her yourself did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Oh yes, yes. Oh yes, we do, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 If you had a worry who would you take it to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, mother - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were you close to your father to \'85
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Or more close to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 He was - well both really - they were both good. And they never knocked us about - no, no. Word of the to
ngue was enough from father - yes. I only remember my father hitting me once - and we was at the table, as I said we weren't allowed to talk, and my brother Sid - dead and gone - I don't know something arose and we started and I went a word too far and I 
can always remember it - my father giving me a clout and he gave me a clout. Now, he says, you'll remember that won't you? And I have remembered it - yes. Mind you it wasn't - he didn't knock us about ordinary but I did - I went a bit too far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 So he wanted to teach you a lesson?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes. And he did too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 But you never had a beating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were you given any other punishments that you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no, not as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What about being sent to bed - that kind of thing - were you sent to bed early or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Well, no, we'd be told to go in the other room - they'd be upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 But you wouldn't have to go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No, no. Not if it wasn't bed time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 What do you think your parents felt were the important things in life to bring their children up to be and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Well, I don't know that. There's one thing about - we was always taught to be honest - yes. Honest and be truthful. And we were taught that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Would you say that those ideas about being honest and truthful that you got more from your mother or from your father or from both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 From both - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 You think they had an equal part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, exactly - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Were there any things you did together as a family - going out anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 
Occasionally - father would take us out to Northwich providing his work had allowed him to get a shilling or two together and he used to - in the summer - that was our one day - only one day - we'd all go out to Northwood - you kn
ow Northwood do you? Well, it's on the Metropolitan line - not so wonderful far out but it was all country, beautiful country, but of course now it's built on like everywhere else - and then we'd go and pick flowers - wild - cowslips, primroses and all th
at sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did your mother go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Yes, yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 Did your mother have any other outings at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1861752 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 No. Oh, if she had a chance and there was a mothers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2039760\charrsid10295177 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177  meeting - the - Mission Hall she might go then providing she hadn't got any work in her confinement business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3739534 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10645759\charrsid10295177 But of course you never know when that's going to happen do you?
